00:36:34.493 --> 00:36:37.680
Trebalo bi biti lako, devojka je grozna.

00:36:37.729 --> 00:36:40.297
Nosi kecelju.

00:36:40.299 --> 00:36:42.299
Poliester.

00:36:42.301 --> 00:36:45.135
Sviđa mi se poliester.

00:36:45.137 --> 00:36:46.703
Imam sastanak.

